I'm trying to get my hands on a copy of the new search results module per <https://developers.HubSpot.com/changelog/new-versions-of-default-cms-site-search-input-and-search-results-modules|this post>

But entering
`@HubSpot/search_results.module --assetVersion=1`
returns the error
`[ERROR] Unknown argument: assetVersion`

Any ideas?
